{"tid":153010,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人用過 chromecast ？","createTime":"2017-03-12T09:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T12:39:17.000Z","uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a16a55a10b9e51b6a0fa24c9318c569eefbec5a2","tid":153010,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"主要想將IPHONE ／IPAD 野射去電視睇，但聽過有啲人話唔係想像中好用<br />\n所以想睇下巴打建唔建議買"},{"pid":"e1ae50ed2d80ad7dda5940231936f64cabb6848b","tid":153010,"uid":60195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"用緊 好似係某d共同既app先射到去電視播？ （youtube/ netlfix) <br />\n我係房用 播netflix 幾正 （房本身無電腦既話）<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 之前申請/續期和記上網送 巴打可以去問下"},{"pid":"2faaacc5fe3176f7ec336a6be5ec22f4e1285e26","tid":153010,"uid":376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"Ipad用翻apple tv會好好多"},{"pid":"96cec77d20add6bda931a2b72e3ceef997c0cfbc","tid":153010,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"Chromecast 應該唔support 用 iPhone mirror, 不如用返airplay"},{"pid":"6614913a5de973b024f73e4ed2e6f9de43e500ca","tid":153010,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊 好似係某d共同既app先射到去電視播？ （youtube/ netlfix) <br />\n我係房用 播netflix 幾正 （房本身無電腦既話）<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 之前申請/續期和記上網送 巴打可以去問下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最令我擔心既就係D無寫出黎既APP<br />\n好似 VIU咁，官網無寫，但UNWIRE又寫左可以做到，不過就話會有停頓"},{"pid":"a4392177a245d0801d1fd8ecc874aeeafc5d42d1","tid":153010,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Chromecast 應該唔support 用 iPhone mirror, 不如用返airplay</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過要留意的是，Chromecast 如配對 Android 手機使用，是可以將手機畫面投射到電視操控；但在 iPhone 上就不支援的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打提醒<br />\n<br />\n不過 APPLE TV好似要成千蚊，唔化算"},{"pid":"a1dea1c1e8e7b68bb66897714ba2cb5c8e8a57ce